{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/notes/how-to-give-box-shadow-border-radius/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Chandler Moisen","author":"Chandler Moisen"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"224bda09-e484-57fb-82a4-3e53affad760","excerpt":"Today I learned how easy it is to apply a border radius to an element’s box shadow: just add  to the element! Allan, my co-founder at Keming, had recently…","html":"<p>Today I learned how easy it is to apply a border radius to an element’s box shadow: just add <code class=\"language-text\">border-radius</code> to the element!</p>\n<p>Allan, my co-founder at <a href=\"https://keming.io\">Keming</a>, had recently overhauled the design our sign-up form to include box shadow with a border radius:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1c85d90bd185638321ecb790a604e3a4/e4611/border-radius-box-shadow.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.8108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"box shadow with border radius\"\n        title=\"box shadow with border radius\"\n        src=\"/static/1c85d90bd185638321ecb790a604e3a4/fcda8/border-radius-box-shadow.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1c85d90bd185638321ecb790a604e3a4/12f09/border-radius-box-shadow.png 148w,\n/static/1c85d90bd185638321ecb790a604e3a4/e4a3f/border-radius-box-shadow.png 295w,\n/static/1c85d90bd185638321ecb790a604e3a4/fcda8/border-radius-box-shadow.png 590w,\n/static/1c85d90bd185638321ecb790a604e3a4/efc66/border-radius-box-shadow.png 885w,\n/static/1c85d90bd185638321ecb790a604e3a4/c83ae/border-radius-box-shadow.png 1180w,\n/static/1c85d90bd185638321ecb790a604e3a4/e4611/border-radius-box-shadow.png 1298w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Initially I thought that this would require modifying the <code class=\"language-text\">box-shadow</code> value in some way, but, much to my surprise and delight, an element’s box shadow will respect and reflect its <code class=\"language-text\">border-radius</code> with no additional work required.</p>\n<p>You can see this in the following CodePen:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://codepen.io/cheshireoctopus/pen/rNObGRP\"><div><iframe \n        height='400' \n        scrolling='no' \n        src='//codepen.io/cheshireoctopus/embed/preview/rNObGRP/?height=400&theme-id=dark&default-tab=html,result' \n        frameborder='no' \n        allowtransparency='true' \n        allowfullscreen='true' \n        style='width: 100%;'></iframe></div></a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to Give Box Shadow a Border Radius","date":"May 25, 2020","isTIL":true}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/how-to-give-box-shadow-border-radius/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/neumorphism/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Neumorphism","redirects":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/put-vs-patch/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"HTTP PUT vs PATCH","redirects":null}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["4173562750","63159454"]}